name: AddDeath
description:
Shadow essence merges with your target as you infuse them with death's transformative finality and spectral power. The spell lasts for 10_minute. It extends to targets up to 100 feet distant. Level 1.

Bloodline Compatibility: Your Death bloodline has 100% affinity with Death magic.

name: AddLove
